query:
SELECT
            warp_standard_light_cones.*,
            light_cones_text.name name
        FROM
            warp_standard_light_cones
        LEFT JOIN
            light_cones_text
        ON
            light_cones_text.id = light_cone AND light_cones_text.language = $2
        WHERE
            uid = $1
        ORDER BY
            timestamp
